<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT73">
<l>ārē yaṟivā raṉaittulaku muṇṭumiḻnta</l>
<l>pērāḻi yāṉṟaṉ perumaiyai kārceṟinta</l>
<l>kaṇṭattā ṉeṇkaṇṇāṉ kāṇā ṉavaṉvaitta</l>
<l>paṇṭaittā ṉattiṉ pati.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who would know the greatness of [the Lord] with the great discus</l>
<l rend="indent">who swallowed and spat out all the worlds?</l>
<l>[Śiva] with the throat dense with blackness [and] the eight-eyed [Brahmā]</l>
<l>Will not perceive the location of the ancient heaven that He had placed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
